pathway.author: [MaintBot, Mkutmon]

comments.content: Adapted from Raza et al. (2008). This pathway is initiated by IFNG binding to its receptor and a subsequent phosphorylation cascade involving a number of the JAK and STAT family of proteins. Several transcriptionally active complexes are formed (STAT1 homodimer, ISGF3 complex, STAT1:STAT1:IRF9 complex) and the pathway culminates with the transcriptional activation of target genes. [1]
This pathway was inferred from Homo sapiens pathway [http://wikipathways.org/instance/WP619_r71168 WP619(71168)]  with a 88.0% conversion rate.
